snippet.title: Did Ancient Indians Pioneer Surgery 10,000 Years Ago?
snippet.description:
A series of archeological and textual evidence of surgery and medical technology in Ancient India. Archeologists have discovered evidence of trepanning and dentistry in India valley civilization going back 10,000 years ago. This is backed by the ancient texts like Sushruta Samhita and Charaka Samhita.

snippet.title: The Prambanan Ramayana - Episode 6
snippet.description:
This episode of Prambanan Ramayana concludes in a very contrasting way. Even if you know The Epic Ramayana well, you are going to be surprised. The unseen carvings of Lava and Kusha are depicted on the walls of Prambanan temple will blow your mind. Did Rama find his sons and reunite with the love of his life? And also, is Valmiki a character in this?

snippet.title: The Prambanan Ramayana - Episode 5
snippet.description:
